Ranger Help for: rscore
=======================

SYNTAX:      rscore (or: rsc)
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Display your full Ranger score report. Shows rank, skill scores,
terrains, stats, and camp information.

FIELDS:
  Rank          Your rank based on skill slots invested
  Ranger XP     Progress toward your next Ranger guild level
  Wilderness    Score from Survival + Cartography + Hunting skills
  Martial       Score from Attack + Archery skills
  Spiritual     Score from Husbandry skills
  Skills        Number learned out of the current skill table
  Slots         Remaining and invested skill slots
  Terrain       Your primary and secondary terrain
  Enemy         Your enemy species (+30% crit bonus)
  Adapt         Arctic or Desert survival specialization
  Follower      Your current bonded animal companion
  Camp          Your camp location (login point)

